set_metric_alias(25.10)                                set_metric_alias(25.10)

Name  set_metric_alias  -  Renames  a metric name, prefixed with the name of a
       layer, analysis view, path group etc, to another name
Syntax
Parameters -from <old_name> Specifies the metric object name  to  be  changed.
       Data_type:  string, required -help Outputs a brief description that in-
       cludes type and default information for each  set_metric_alias  parame-
       ter.  For  a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
       ters, use the man command: man set_metric_alias. -no_overwrite   Speci-
       fies  to  not overwrite an already set alias. Data_type: bool, optional
       -order <order_of_priority> Specifies the order of  priority  of  metric
       object in tables. Data_type: int, optional -to <new_name> Specifies the
       new name for the metric object. Data_type: string, required
Example
